'''[[gum]] [[arabic]]'''

#An edible substance taken from one of two species of sub-saharan [[acacia]] trees.  It is used in the food industry as a stabilizer (e.g. in [[soda]], [[gumdrop]]s and [[marshmallows]]) and in other industries including pharmaceuticals, paints and polishs.

===Synonyms===
